object.script:
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() x = input.getNumber(1) y = input.getNumber(2) zoom = input.getNumber(3) end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.drawMap(x, y, zoom) screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawLine(w/2 + 1, h/2, w/2 - 2, h/2) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2 + 1, w/2, h/2 - 2) end

object.script:
function onTick() isPressed = input.getBool(1) inputx = input.getNumber(3) inputy = input.getNumber(4) frontTilt = input.getNumber(5) * 4 * 90 sideTilt = input.getNumber(6) * 4 * 90 end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() rad = w + h cx = w/2 cy = h/2 pitch = math.acos(frontTilt / 180) roll = math.rad(90 - sideTilt) troll = math.rad(0 - sideTilt) broll = math.rad(180 - sideTilt) x1 = cx + rad * math.cos(roll + pitch) y1 = cy + rad * math.sin(roll + pitch) x2 = cx + rad * math.cos(roll - pitch) y2 = cy + rad * math.sin(roll - pitch) x3 = cx + rad * math.cos(troll - pitch) y3 = cy + rad * math.sin(troll - pitch) x4 = cx + rad * math.cos(broll - pitch) y4 = cy + rad * math.sin(broll - pitch) screen.drawLine(x1, y1, x2, y2)
screen.setColor(94, 60, 34) --brown screen.drawTriangleF(x1, y1, x2, y2, x4, y4) screen.setColor(40, 114, 151) --blue screen.drawTriangleF(x1, y1, x2, y2, x3, y3)
screen.setColor(200, 200, 200) screen.drawTriangleF(cx + 10, cy, cx, cy + 10, cx - 10, cy) screen.drawRectF(cx - 10, cy - 5, 20, 5) end

function onTick() isPressed = input.getBool(1) inputx = input.getNumber(3) inputy = input.getNumber(4) frontTilt = input.getNumber(5) * 4 * 90 sideTilt = input.getNumber(6) * 4 * 90 end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() rad = w + h cx = w/2 cy = h/2 pitch = math.acos(frontTilt / 180) roll = math.rad(90 - sideTilt) troll = math.rad(0 - sideTilt) broll = math.rad(180 - sideTilt) x1 = cx + rad * math.cos(roll + pitch) y1 = cy + rad * math.sin(roll + pitch) x2 = cx + rad * math.cos(roll - pitch) y2 = cy + rad * math.sin(roll - pitch) x3 = cx + rad * math.cos(troll - pitch) y3 = cy + rad * math.sin(troll - pitch) x4 = cx + rad * math.cos(broll - pitch) y4 = cy + rad * math.sin(broll - pitch) screen.drawLine(x1, y1, x2, y2)
screen.setColor(94, 60, 34) --brown screen.drawTriangleF(x1, y1, x2, y2, x4, y4) screen.setColor(40, 114, 151) --blue screen.drawTriangleF(x1, y1, x2, y2, x3, y3)
screen.setColor(200, 200, 200) screen.drawTriangleF(cx + 10, cy, cx + 5, cy + 5, cx + 5, cy) screen.drawRectF(cx - 10, cy - 5, 20, 5) screen.drawRectF(cx - 10, cy, 15, 5) end
